com.bonitasoft.engine.page

Interface Page

  • All Superinterfaces:
    BaseElement, BonitaObject, Serializable

    public interface Page
extends BaseElement
    A Page is a way to store, amongst other things, a binary content. It is used by Bonita BPM Portal to display specific custom content
    Author:
    Laurent Leseigneur
